## `DeclareDesign`

### Topics



```{r, eval = FALSE, echo = TRUE}
mean <- 1
simplest_design <-
  
  declare_model(N = 100, Y = rnorm(N, mean)) +
  
  declare_inquiry(Q = mean) +
  
  declare_estimator(Y ~ 1)
```

